          "start": 0,
          "end": 9
        },
        "kind": "semantic",
        "text": "不尚賢，不貴奇，不見異物，民則安於本分，不爭、不盜、不亂。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "hesonggong-2",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 3,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 24
        },
        "kind": "semantic",
        "text": "聖人治國，使民虛心實腹，弱志強骨，常使民無知無欲。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "hesonggong-3",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 5,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 16
        },
        "kind": "semantic",
        "text": "使智者不敢為非，則天下無不治矣。",
        "source": "cham"
      }
    ],
